} else if (opp === 'PAGE_2_STRUGGLE') {
  task = `The page is on page 2 (pos ${item.avg_position}) for "${item.top_query}". It needs more content depth to break into page 1.

Generate:
- new_h2: an H2 section heading that directly answers a search query a fleet manager would type when looking for "${item.top_query}". Phrase as a question or specific claim.
- new_section_body: 200-400 words of substantive content under that H2. Include 2-3 specific numbers/examples (capacity ranges, real fleet sizes, contract specifics). MUST be in Paul's voice — no marketing fluff.
